xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.application-boundary-social-construction"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085507","id":"zettel.20260420085507","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1296},"end":{"line":21,"column":52,"offset":1345},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085507","id":"zettel.20260420085507","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420085349","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1396},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1421},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085349"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":3,"offset":2693},"end":{"line":39,"column":28,"offset":2718},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085714","id":"zettel.20260420085714","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1561},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1586},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085834","id":"zettel.20260420085834","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":3,"offset":1646},"end":{"line":23,"column":28,"offset":1671},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420090017","id":"zettel.20260420090017","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1354},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1379},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420090203","id":"zettel.20260420090203","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1429},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1454},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":3,"offset":2858},"end":{"line":46,"column":28,"offset":2883},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420085507"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"boundary-aplikasi-adalah-konstruksi-sosial-bukan-fakta-alam\">Boundary aplikasi adalah konstruksi sosial, bukan fakta alam<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#boundary-aplikasi-adalah-konstruksi-sosial-bukan-fakta-alam\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"The first problem with defining application architecture is that there's no clear definition of what an application is. My view is that applications are a social construction: a body of code that's seen by developers as a single unit, a group of functionality that business customers see as a single unit, and an initiative that those with the money see as a single budget.\"</p>\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/architecture/\">https://martinfowler.com/architecture/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fowler menempatkan masalah application architecture pertama kali pada ketidakjelasan definisi \"application\".</li>\n<li>Aplikasi bukan fakta alam; dia muncul dari cara developer, bisnis, dan pemegang anggaran mengelompokkan sebuah unit.</li>\n<li>Karena definisi unitnya berbeda, debat batas sistem sering macet meski orang merasa membahas hal yang sama.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diskusi arsitektur harus diawali dengan klarifikasi konteks: apa yang dianggap sebagai satu aplikasi oleh setiap pihak.</li>\n<li>Boundary aplikasi perlu dilihat sebagai hasil konsensus sosial, bukan kriteria teknis tunggal.</li>\n<li>Pilihan arsitektural seperti microservices atau monolith harus mempertimbangkan perspektif pengelompokan kerja, fungsi, dan biaya.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.application-boundary-social-construction\">Application boundary adalah konstruksi sosial</a> — literature note tentang ide aplikasi sebagai social construction</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — ringkasan halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420085349\">Keputusan arsitektural penting bergantung pada skala sistem</a> — keputusan arsitektural penting bergantung pada skala sistem</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">application-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">martin-fowler (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420085714\">Aplikasi tetap ada karena boundary adalah unit sosial dan ekonomi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420085834\">Microservices adalah trade-off machine, bukan arsitektur modern otomatis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420090017\">Modernisasi yang matang adalah displacement bertahap, bukan rewrite besar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420090203\">Micro Frontends menunjukkan arsitektur juga soal koordinasi tim</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":nul